# Dialogue hint
- Author: Gardemarin
- Game: skyrimspecialedition
- Mod Page: https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/30182


My previous work: [GOLD LACK](https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/30018)
  
![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
  
  
  
Now, whenever the game checks the level of your eloquence skill, a hint is built into the dialogue, dialogs have also been added to the mod which do not check the level of eloquence skill but disguise themselves as such.
  
I also added dialogs marked with a lie, although Bethesda did not implement a test of eloquence, implying that the NPCs unconditionally believe player. Just for fun.
